@startuml sq_sbx02_apply_sandbox_policy
' ============================================================
' Title:     SBX-02 — APPLY Sandbox Policy
' Boundary:  nasim code agent
' Purpose:   Load and apply sandbox security policy
' Milestone: v1.0
' Version:   1.0.0
